OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1776066987
OL,3,CIrish police break up oil refinery
OL,4,Cprotest as country rocked by fuel
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FPolice have removed protesters from
OL,8,Fkey infrastructure points across
OL,9,FIreland, ITV News Correspondent Graham
OL,10,FStothard reports
OL,12,FPolice removed and arrested protesters
OL,13,Fon Saturday to reopen Ireland's only
OL,14,Foil refinery, as a fifth day of
OL,15,Fdisruptive demonstrations over the
OL,16,Fsoaring price of fuel left many gas
OL,17,Fpumps dry and threatened to cripple
OL,18,Ftransportation across the country.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
