OL,3,CIrish police break up oil refinery
OL,4,Cprotest as country rocked by fuel
OL,5,Cshortages
OL,7,FAt midday, police vans from the public
OL,8,Forder unit rolled into Whitegate
OL,9,Frefinery in County Cork, the country's
OL,10,Fonly oil refinery, to clear the
OL,11,Fprotesters as the military stood by to
OL,12,Fassist. Officers used pepper spray,
OL,13,Fand video on RTE showed several
OL,14,Fofficers dragging a protester from a
OL,15,Ftractor.
OL,17,FA convoy of seven fuel delivery trucks
OL,18,Ffrom different companies was escorted
OL,19,Fto the refinery to load up and was
OL,20,Flater seen leaving.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
